creator: Yumasoft Inc.
descriptionHtml: The Millside Restaurant is a family run business situated in the rural village of Cloughmills & Rathkenny, just off the A26 between Ballymoney and Ballymena. The Millside first opened its doors in November 2004 and has gone from strength to strength to become the 75 seated restaurant it is today. We now also have two fully functioning takeaways from both of our locations. For ease of ordering, we offer a user-friendly app and website. We have an excellent range of menus including breakfast, lunch and dinner. We can provide a separate function and party menu for larger parties at very competitive rates.
descriptionShort: Pizza pasta takeaway located In both Cloughmills & Rathkenny. Northern Ireland
